  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1014">
<l>aṇiyaṉṟō nāṇuṭaimai cāṉṟōrk kaḵtiṉṟēṟ </l>
<l>piṇiyaṉṟō pīṭu naṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is not the modesty ornament of the noble ? Without it, their haughtiness would be a pain (to others).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
